metadata.name: Bafflëdframz #42
metadata.description: Losing sight of the original objective Deviate from scales Jump fences and cross borders. Continue in this direction despite the disorganization. However, I took the trouble to draw a well-detailed plan and shape in order to arrive at a clean and well-structured result. But, I got lost again...I lost my bearings. I lost the GridesThis is what Bafflëdframz stands for. A well-structured work plan, but emotions pushed my creativity away from the structure. I finally lost my starting grids.
